descriptor.name: Original Almond Butter: Crunchy
descriptor.short_desc: Introducing MyFitness Original Almond Butter - the perfect blend of pure almonds with a desi twist for a unique and delicious taste. It is made with 89% almonds, which are carefully selected and roasted to perfection. The spread tastes subtly sweet with a hint of saltiness, making it the perfect spread for toast, or even as a dip for fruits & vegatables. Not only is MyFitness natural almond butter delicious, but it is also known to have several health benefits. The healthy fats in almonds can help lower cholesterol levels, improve heart health, and even aid in weight loss. The magnesium and potassium in almonds can also help regulate blood pressure and support bone health.In addition, MyFitness almond butter is gluten-free, non-GMO, and made with no artificial ingredients. Try this delicious spread today & enjoy the taste and benefits of pure, natural almonds.n

descriptor.name: MyFitness Schezwan Peanut Butter: Smooth
descriptor.short_desc: Introducing MyFitness Schezwan Peanut Butter - A Spicy Twist to Your Favorite Spread!Want to take your taste buds on a fiery ride? Then get ready to savor our latest spread- MyFitness Schezwan Peanut Butter.This one-of-a-kind blend combines the smooth and velvety peanut butter with the Fiery kick of Schezwan. This fantastic fusion will tantalize your taste buds like never before and add an unforgettable kick to your meals and snacks. Key Features:Fiery Fusion - The irresistible allure of Schezwan combined with the creamy goodness of peanut butter feels like a match made in culinary heaven. Natural Ingredients - We prioritize quality & taste by using only the finest quality ingredients in our Peanut Butter. This ensures that you get a pure, authentic flavor experience with every bite.Loved by All - MyFitness Schezwan Peanut Butter is loved by people of all ages. The unique flavor profile appeals to both children and adults, making it a versatile addition to meals and snacks.Nutrient-Rich - Packed with protein, healthy fats, and essential vitamins & minerals, our Schezwan Peanut Butter offers a nutritious boost while keeping you satisfied for longer.Gluten-Free & Vegan-Friendly: Our Schezwan Peanut Butter is gluten-free, making it suitable for individuals with dietary preferences. Moreover, it is also vegan-friendly, making it a delicious option for those following a plant-based diet.Resealable Packaging - Designed with convenience in mind, our Schezwan Peanut Butter comes in a resealable jar. This ensures that the product stays fresh, so you can enjoy it at your own pace without any concern about the quality.How to Use it:Spread it: You can spread it on your toast for a fiery morning breakfast or as a savory evening snack. Dip it: You can use it as a zesty dip with veggies nuts, crackers, chicken wings/ strips for an unforgettable snacking experience.Sizzle it up: Enhance your stir-fries, sauces, or marinades with a dollop of Schezwan Peanut Butter for a flavorful fiery burst. Order your jar today and experience the perfect spicy nutty harmony in every bite!
